SOURCE: https://github.com/uber/baseweb/blob/main/documentation-site/pages/guides/theming.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { Button } from "baseui/button";

function App() {
  return (
    <Button
      overrides={{
        BaseButton: {
          style: ({ $theme }) => {
            return {
              marginTop: $theme.sizing.scale500,
            };
          },
        },
      }}
    />
  );
}
```

