TITLE: Disabling Touch Scrolling with JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This JavaScript snippet disables touch scrolling by preventing default touch events.  It adds a touchstart event listener to the document and calls `e.preventDefault()` for each event. The listener must be non-passive to allow `preventDefault()` to work.
