TITLE: Modal Component with Paragraph Wrapping - React
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates a Modal component implemented with Button for triggering visibility. It follows SEO practices by ensuring that text within the ModalBody is wrapped in a paragraph, aiding search engine visibility.
SOURCE: https://github.com/uber/baseweb/blob/main/documentation-site/pages/guides/seo.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: JavaScript
