TITLE: Migrating Tab Component - diff
DESCRIPTION: Requires migration from using the 'TabPanel' component to directly using the 'Tab' component for consistency and reducing unnecessary component layers. This change simplifies the tab structure under 'StatefulTabs'.
SOURCE: https://github.com/uber/baseweb/blob/main/documentation-site/pages/blog/base-web-v7/index.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_12

LANGUAGE: diff
CODE:
```
<StatefulTabs initialState={{activeKey: '0'}}>\n- <TabPanel title=\"Tab Link 1\">Tab 1 content</TabPanel>\n+ <Tab title=\"Tab Link 1\">Tab 1 content</Tab>\n</StatefulTabs>
```

